Class SoyJavaSrcFunctionUtils

java.lang.Object
  com.google.template.soy.javasrc.restricted.SoyJavaSrcFunctionUtils

public class SoyJavaSrcFunctionUtils
extends Object

Utilities for implementing SoyJavaSrcFunctions.

Important: This class may only be used in implementing plugins (e.g. functions, directives).

Feel free to static import these helpers in your function implementation classes.
